•	Which elements are flung into space from CCSNe?
•	Based on the pictures, are CCSNe spherically symmetric processes?
 
Gravitational Waves:
•	Read the first 2 paragraphs of the introduction in this paper
•	https://academic.oup.com/ptps/article/doi/10.1143/PTPS.128.183/1930275
•	In your own words, how do theory, observation, and computation (what we do) relate?
•	Find the equations for h+ and hx; how do they depend on angle?
•	Watch the video below that visualizes the GW emission from BHs (this will be similar to our end goal, but with CCSNe)
•	https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-01153-7
